    "description": "East Wind is a co-op survival trading game that takes place in a cozy world with lots to discover. Whether alone or with friends, you will gather resources, craft items, and embark on a journey to trade your goods.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hand Crafted Open World</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/ae7cc3e67ed9b56a8eda260859663469.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/ae7cc3e67ed9b56a8eda260859663469.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/ae7cc3e67ed9b56a8eda260859663469.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dive into an open world made by hand, filled with surprises at every turn.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single Player and Online Co-Op</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/0b78a783e2b3482036f08ffe0e511b6f.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/0b78a783e2b3482036f08ffe0e511b6f.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/0b78a783e2b3482036f08ffe0e511b6f.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Embark on your journey either as a lone wolf or with buddies by your side, because everything's better with friends!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Resource Gathering</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/2cb7a910bcb4b1c6f872469af8a4f39d.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/2cb7a910bcb4b1c6f872469af8a4f39d.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/2cb7a910bcb4b1c6f872469af8a4f39d.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect valuable resources to aid you on your journey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/1f8b15cbbed821a3ef469cf346764cc2.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/1f8b15cbbed821a3ef469cf346764cc2.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/1f8b15cbbed821a3ef469cf346764cc2.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use what you’ve collected to create useful items, key to your success.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trading</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/ec5cbedadd0bceac0de87af62dfca4a5.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/ec5cbedadd0bceac0de87af62dfca4a5.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/ec5cbedadd0bceac0de87af62dfca4a5.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Venture into towns to trade your goods for needed supplies or rare items.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Navigation &amp; Boat Building</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/74c495cec57042bd0eaffbf1f8f7f300.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/74c495cec57042bd0eaffbf1f8f7f300.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/74c495cec57042bd0eaffbf1f8f7f300.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Construct your dream boat and sail the open ocean.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Missions</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/508d50d57c2b6e8fc50b2a0c3ac9fb2c.poster.avif?t=1761569135\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/508d50d57c2b6e8fc50b2a0c3ac9fb2c.webm?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203830/extras/508d50d57c2b6e8fc50b2a0c3ac9fb2c.mp4?t=1761569135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take on missions to earn rewards and keep the excitement going strong.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Day &amp; Night Cycle with Seasons</h2>Watch the cycle of day and night paint the skies as seasons shift, impacting your journey.<br><br><br>Brace yourself. There’s an East Wind coming.",
